{"tid":1265470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東涌地盤鋁板高處墮下 擊斃工人","createTime":"2019-06-29T07:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T07:56:54.000Z","uid":163502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e8861f89b020f62acd4f7e6f495a6874021f59c4","tid":1265470,"uid":163502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T07:56:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1533645/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%9D%B1%E6%B6%8C%E5%9C%B0%E7%9B%A4%E9%8B%81%E6%9D%BF%E9%AB%98%E8%99%95%E5%A2%AE%E4%B8%8B-%E6%93%8A%E6%96%83%E5%B7%A5%E4%BA%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1533645%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%259D%25B1%25E6%25B6%258C%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%259B%25A4%25E9%258B%2581%25E6%259D%25BF%25E9%25AB%2598%25E8%2599%2595%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E4%25B8%258B-%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%2596%2583%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BA%25BA&d=FYZ0PdCaIZeH%2BWUkJYSmqy2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=a4f175a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1533645%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%259D%25B1%25E6%25B6%258C%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%259B%25A4%25E9%258B%2581%25E6%259D%25BF%25E9%25AB%2598%25E8%2599%2595%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E4%25B8%258B-%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%2596%2583%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BA%25BA&h=2da03c05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1533645/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%9D%B1%E6%B6%8C%E5%9C%B0%E7%9B%A4%E9%8B%81%E6%9D%BF%E9%AB%98%E8%99%95%E5%A2%AE%E4%B8%8B-%E6%93%8A%E6%96%83%E5%B7%A5%E4%BA%BA</a><br />\n<br />\n東涌迎禧路一個地盤發生工業意外，一名男工人遭鋁板擊中受傷，送院經搶救後不治。<br />\n<br />\n事發在下午1時許，有工人在運送約10多塊鋁板時，疑有人鬆手，整批鋁板突由3米高位置墮下，一名38歲姓蘇的男工人走避不及被擊中頭部，當場重傷昏迷，工友報警求助。消防及救護員到場將他救出，並由救護車送往北大嶼山醫院搶救，惜終告不治。警方正展開調查，初步相信無可疑，列作工業意外處理，勞工處人員亦到場了解。"}]}